---

## 3. Markov Regime Walker
Synthetic return series driven by a hidden Markov model.
- 3 regimes: trending, mean-reverting, high-vol chop
- Color overlay on price chart shows hidden state
- Side panel: transition matrix heatmap
- Sliders for each regime's drift / vol / MR speed
